Package: scPathway
Type: Package
Title: Lightweight Pathway Analysis for Single-Cell RNA-seq
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("James", "Woo", email = "james@example.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Author: James Woo [aut, cre]
Maintainer: James Woo <james@example.com>
Description: A lightweight, matrix-native toolkit for pathway scoring and comparison
    in single-cell RNA-seq data with optional Seurat v5 input compatibility.
    Supports cell-level exploratory analysis and sample-level formal inference.
